{
  "stem": "3928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which is-- as long as they were with me, we were fine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As soon as left me, you know, they became the same people who was always before, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were hating people-- people for no reason at all, except, what I called it, because, by God's grace, they were born the wrong race or the wrong religion according to them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in 1938, when I heard this broadcast and when Hitler marched into Czechoslovakia, I felt, you know, that the end will come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we have to face the fact.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know some people, through the union, because my uncle was involved with the union.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were, naturally, anti-Nazis, at least 98% of them, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they formed-- they said, if we have to, we form a resistance movement, and we do what we can to try to keep the Germans out of here and help the people if anybody get persecuted, you know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I joined this group then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first meeting was in Csepel Island, with this group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this was the strongest-- the stronghold of the union because of the factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were 30,000 people worked in this factory at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a majority of them wasn't unionized, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a part which was unionized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was, because of my background, of my uncle, I was able to get contact with these people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we did-- from this day on, we worked everything to try to help the resistance movement and whatever we can do in order to help the Allied effort.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, at the time, there was no American involvement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was only involvement the French and the English, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we tried to do everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
